p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">今年社会捐助活动仍围绕&ldquo;送温暖、献爱心&rdquo;主题，充分发挥各级党政机关干部和共产党员的带头作用，广泛动员社会各界和广大人民群众，弘扬团结互助、扶贫济困的中华美德，为困难群众特别是受灾特困户提供援助，为因灾缺粮户给予口粮救助，并为困难群众募集过冬棉衣被。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">二、时间安排<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">捐助活动从<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2011</span>年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">25</span>日开始，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15</span>日前完成捐助资金和棉衣被的接收工作，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>日前完成资金分配和衣被发放工作，确保困难群众温暖过冬。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">三、捐助标准<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">要求行政事业单位干部职工都要捐款。标准为：县级干部每人捐资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>元，局级干部每人捐资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>元，一般干部和职工每人捐资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">80</span>元。同时号召广大干部职工每人捐一件衣，每户捐一床棉絮。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">四、组织形式<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">县民政局负责社会捐助活动的组织协调工作，捐助的资金由县财政局负责收集，政府统一安排使用。捐助的衣被由各单位负责组织收集，并送到各单位联点村。宣传部门负责社会捐助活动的宣传工作。要大力宣传党中央、国务院和省委、省政府对灾区及贫困地区群众的关怀，宣传党政军机关和党员干部、广大人民群众&ldquo;送温暖、献爱心&rdquo;的感人事迹，营造人人关心困难群众的氛围，广泛动员社会各界参与捐助活动，弘扬&ldquo;一方有难、八方支援&rdquo;的中华民族传统美德。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">五、活动要求<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）高度重视，加强领导。各单位要牢牢把握立党为公、执政为民的本质要求和全心全意为人民服务的根本宗旨，以高度的政治责任感，把这次&ldquo;送温暖、献爱心&rdquo;活动抓紧抓落实。各单位要认真组织实施，各级党员领导干部要带头捐助，起到表率作用。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）精心组织，周密部署。各单位要认真做好动员部署工作，营造良好舆论氛围，迅速掀起捐助热潮，让困难群众感受到党和政府的关怀，感受到社会主义大家庭的温暖。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）坚持自愿和量力而行原则。这次捐助活动以捐款为主，也可以捐赠棉被、大衣、羽绒服、毛衣、毛裤、绒衣裤、棉衣裤等御寒衣被。所有捐款，重点用于解决困难灾民和困难职工的生活救助。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-fa