-color: transparent; border-top-color: windowtext; width: 85pt; height: 39pt; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\"><strong>服务办理时限</strong></td>\r\n            <td width=\"532\" x:str=\"20个工作日 \" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: windowtext; width: 399pt; border-left-color: windowtext; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\">20个工作日&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr height=\"52\" style=\"height: 39pt\">\r\n            <td height=\"52\" width=\"113\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 0.5pt solid; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: windowtext; width: 85pt; height: 39pt; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\"><strong>收费标准</strong></td>\r\n            <td width=\"532\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: windowtext; width: 399pt; border-left-color: windowtext; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\">不收费</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr height=\"52\" style=\"height: 39pt\">\r\n            <td height=\"52\" width=\"113\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 0.5pt solid; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: windowtext; width: 85pt; height: 39pt; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\"><strong>表格下载</strong></td>\r\n            <td width=\"532\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: windowtext; width: 399pt; border-left-color: windowtext; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\">暂无表格模版</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr height=\"52\" style=\"height: 39pt\">\r\n            <td height=\"52\" width=\"113\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 0.5pt solid; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: windowtext; width: 85pt; height: 39pt; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\"><strong>备注</strong></td>\r\n            <td width=\"532\" style=\"border-bottom: win